com.phonegap.calendar.android.adapters
Class Event

java.lang.Object
  com.phonegap.calendar.android.adapters.Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable

This class represents a Calendar event object, really is not implementing any operation, apart from build the EventEntry from Event object and viceversa, but this object there will be used in order to be persisted in the user calendar.

Author:
Sergio Martinez Rodriguez
